If you specify the &lt;code&gt;&quot;%.1f&quot;&lt;/code&gt; format before the &lt;code&gt;set table&lt;/code&gt; command your data in &lt;code&gt;equipotential_lines.txt&lt;/code&gt; will change and be cut after the first decimal place. That is the reason while it no longer looks smooth.

